parameters:
\SE[3]I am grateful that you have accepted this proposal.
\!\SE[46]It seems that Chairman Caudain has a keen eye.

\SE[2]Since our interests align, there is no reason to
refuse.

\SE[38]Moreover, if Your Highness is prepared to sacrifice
your life... \SE[1]I cannot treat such a precious
determination... disrespectfully.

\SE[56]Do you... think that you will definitely win?
\SE[33]Very well. See for yourself that I am not just all
talk... \SE[54]Witness that I am not just a smooth-talking
girl!

\SE[3]Oh, what's this...? \SE[38]Hehe, it seems like it'll
be a good side show...!

(So it has come to this after all...! Princess, please be
safe...!!)

\SE[0]...No, it was beyond my expectations. You are not just
a smooth-talking girl. \SE[38] You seem to be someone who
has a mission and stands above others.

\SE[39]That's why... It's unfortunate. \SE[36]I now have a
reason to dispose of you here without fail.

\SE[53]That... is an honor. \!\SE[51]However, as an
evaluation of me, it is still insufficient!

\SE[38]From your disciple, I have received a deadly plan for
times like this... \SE[54]Witness my Aurora Flash with your
own eyes...!!

\SE[38]Hehe... You've been through a lot. \SE[37]While
minimizing the damage and buying time... You've fulfilled
all the responsibilities of someone who stands above others.

\SE[0]I will return to the castle. \.I leave the aftermath
to you.
